title.narrative:
HRD investigations supported by software tools demonstrably lead to:
- Perpetrators being held to account to deter future violations;
- Achieve justice for victims through reparations, memorialisation, policy change, brought about by institutions that are open to all;
- Collective memory of the past brings societies to heal and grow into a better future.

